I find nothing in the REST style that addresses Status Codes. However,
there are some detailed rules in the HTTP 1.1docs (RFC2616) addressing
the use of the message body:

Method Definitions:
http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2616#section-9

Status Code Definitons:
http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2616#section-10

mca
